      "text": "Done by ChatGPT … no gerrymandering … GOP blows away Democrats in the House. \n\nInstructions and Constraints to ChatGPT…\n\nDraw a Congressional map with the following guidelines:\n\n** Apportion seats by population (761,000 People Per District).\n\n** Draw compact contiguous districts.\n\n** No odd shapes.  Districts should be as regular shapes as possible.\n\n** Whole counties as much as possible. \n\n** Adjacent or adjoining counties when possible. \n\n** Only one county or part of one county where possible. \n\n** No partisan considerations.\n\n** No illegal aliens or non-citizens. \n\n** No racial considerations.\n\n** Draw districts as closely as possible to what America's founders envisioned when they wrote and ratified the Constitution of the United States.\n\nAll U.S. citizens (children + adults) — citizens only, excluding non-citizens, but including minors",
